  ('medical-tech-moex-17773', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-096-05118730', 'sub-medical-tech-09', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於Corynebacterium diphtheriae致病力的敘述，何者正確？', '["此菌雖未侵入血液，卻可能引起全身症狀", "主要的毒力因子是一種A-B endotoxin", "高濃度鐵離子可誘導diphtheria toxin之合成", "diphtheria toxin可與ribosome之rRNA結合，抑制蛋白質之合成"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c1b8543e6e72", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0579d7726f66", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096040", "c": "105", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學及臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫、心理、呼吸治療、營養師、獸醫人員考試暨醫師分試考試第一試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
